<div class="modal fade welcome-modal" id="welcomeModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="welcomeModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="welcomeModalLabel">Welcome to Cinematch!</h4>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="text-center p-3 mb-3">
          <img src="<%= asset_path "logos/cm_logo1_glare1.svg" %>" alt="Welcome to Cinematch" class="img-fluid w-60" style="max-height: 150px; max-width: 80%; object-fit: cover;">
        </div>
        <div>Hello, <%= current_user.name %>! We're excited to help you discover your perfect content matches.</div>
        <div class="mt-3">Our two-stage survey process helps us understand you better:</div>
        <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3">
          <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3 p-3" style="background-color: rgba(233, 255, 249, 0.1); border-radius: 0.5rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-1 fa-lg me-3" style="color: var(--jonquil);"></i>
            <span><strong style="color: var(--jonquil);">Basic Survey:</strong> Quick personality assessment and genre preferences (5-7 minutes)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-2 p-3" style="background-color: rgba(233, 255, 249, 0.1); border-radius: 0.5rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-2 fa-lg me-3" style="color: var(--jonquil);"></i>
            <span><strong style="color: var(--jonquil);">Extended Survey:</strong> Optional deeper psychological profile for more precise matches (15-20 minutes)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-3"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle me-2" style="color: var(--jonquil);"></i><strong>Answering the questions genuinely is important for the quality of matches!</strong></div>
        <div class="mt-3">Let's start with the basic survey to get your initial recommendations!</div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn nav-button complete-button" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Start Basic Survey</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 
